  "(?i)You critically hit (?:\\((?<mult>x\\d+)\\) )?for (?<dmg>\\d+) damage with your (?<weapon>.+?)!": "Вы нанесли КРИТ ({mult}) на {dmg} ед. урона вашим {weapon}!",
